{"tid":1702003,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《花木蘭》劉亦菲入選2019荷里活新星","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T18:52:28.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9221e97551d7e67ade2ed984b460c42b0864edbd","tid":1702003,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"《好萊塢報導》（The Hollywood Reporter）近日公布了「2019好萊塢新星」名單，其中華人圈唯一入榜的女演員就是飾演迪士尼真人版《花木蘭》的女星─劉亦菲。<br />\n<br />\n電影《花木蘭》從預告發布後就因「過度改編」引發了不小的負評，到女主角劉亦菲在社群上轉發「我支持香港警察，你們可以打我了 What a shame for Hong Kong」的圖文引來許多歐美網友揚言抵制，最近又傳出該片將大規模重拍，這部電影的產出過程可以說是問題不斷、困難重重。<br />\n<br />\n雖然發生了這麼多不順的事情，但是劉亦菲仍然入選了2019好萊塢新星的名單，這也足見了她現在在電影圈有著一定程度的影響力。除了是華人圈唯一入榜的女演員外，她亦是名單中年紀最長的明星，而名單中年紀最小的則是今年18歲的伊莎貝拉莫娜（Isabela Merced）。<br />\n<br />\n而在報導中，劉亦菲表示她最想與導演戴倫艾洛諾夫斯基（Darren Aronofsky）合作、早上起床第一個打開的App是通訊軟體微信、去KTV會唱冰雪奇緣的主題曲〈Let It Go〉，而最欣賞的明星是娜塔莉波曼（Natalie Portman）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/11/07/99/7036780.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F11%2F07%2F99%2F7036780.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=21b40d36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e890f0e4618459a5dd521d2d21bf532cc8aecdde","tid":1702003,"uid":337826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"臭西"},{"pid":"a6fd148367dbaa69d1f9219c40487e46dafbe60c","tid":1702003,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手Rt + like </span><br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott嘅tweet嚴重唔夠人推，佢係法案好主要嘅推手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=21e974ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006&h=b1cbde8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006</a><br />\n<br />\nSenator Rubio盡心盡力，迫McConnell迫到咁緊都係唔夠多推，希望大家可以幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=e03f2a67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&h=d2de161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846</a>"},{"pid":"4e1bb3752863bef31d83382c9b4c216fd87e5d93","tid":1702003,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb3f7f68731d962eaa60f0a986dd4a72fd11e67","tid":1702003,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:52:28.000Z","msg":"32歲(新星)"}]}